==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Revolver
<hw>Re*volv"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or that
which, revolves; specifically, a firearm ( commonly a pistol) with
several chambers or barrels so arranged as to revolve on an axis, and be
discharged in succession by the same lock; a repeater.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Revolving</ent>⟦br⟧
